#: /home/carloratm/progetti/postgresql-source/doc-9.0.4/libpq.xml:6340(para)
msgid "The file uses an <quote>INI file</quote> format where the section name is the service name and the parameters are connection parameters; see <xref linkend=\"libpq-connect\"/> for a list. For example: <placeholder-1/> An example file is provided at <filename>share/pg_service.conf.sample</filename>."
